== Births == * {{ill|Kenchō|ja|建暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1249]] [[July 9]]) – {{ill|Kameyama Tennō|ja|亀山天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 90th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1305]]). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1868]] [[July 16]]) – {{ill|Hirose Takeo|ja|広瀬武夫|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a member of the {{ill|Navy|ja|海軍|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and a military personnel who became known as the first {{ill|Military Deity|ja|軍神|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} during the {{ill|Russo-Japanese War|ja|日露戦争|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1904]]).
