== Events == * {{ill|Tenpyō|ja|天平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 15th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[743]] [[June 23]]) – {{ill|Konten Einnei Shizaihō|ja|墾田永年私財法|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} の勅令。開墾した土地の私有を許可. * {{ill|Juei|ja|寿永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1182]] [[June 29]]) – 兵乱と {{ill|Sangō no Yaku|ja|三合の厄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} を避ける為、{{ill|Yōwa|ja|養和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} より {{ill|Juei|ja|寿永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} に {{ill|Era change|ja|改元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Eiwa|ja|永和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year/{{ill|Tenshu|ja|天授|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1375]] [[June 26]]) – {{ill|Southern Court|ja|南朝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が {{ill|Bunchū|ja|文中|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} より {{ill|Tenshu|ja|天授|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} に {{ill|Era change|ja|改元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year (閏5月) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1846]] [[July 20]]) – The American East India Squadron commander, Admiral {{ill|James Biddle|ja|ジェームズ・ビドル|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, arrives in Uraga and requests trade. The shogunate refuses.
== Births == * {{ill|Kenchō|ja|建暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1249]] [[July 9]]) – {{ill|Kameyama Tennō|ja|亀山天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 90th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1305]]). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1868]] [[July 16]]) – {{ill|Hirose Takeo|ja|広瀬武夫|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a member of the {{ill|Navy|ja|海軍|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and a military personnel who became known as the first {{ill|Military Deity|ja|軍神|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} during the {{ill|Russo-Japanese War|ja|日露戦争|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1904]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Bun'ei|ja|文永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1273]] [[June 13]]) – {{ill|Hōjō Masamura|ja|北条政村|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 7th {{ill|Shikken|ja|執権|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of the {{ill|Kamakura shogunate|ja|鎌倉幕府|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born [[1205]]).
