== Births == * {{ill|Kenchō|ja|建暦|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1249]] [[July 9]]) – {{ill|Kameyama Tennō|ja|亀山天皇|qq=}}, the 90th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|qq=}} (died [[1305]]). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1868]] [[July 16]]) – {{ill|Hirose Takeo|ja|広瀬武夫|qq=}}, a member of the {{ill|Navy|ja|海軍|qq=}} and a military personnel who became known as the first {{ill|Military Deity|ja|軍神|qq=}} during the {{ill|Russo-Japanese War|ja|日露戦争|qq=}} (died [[1904]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Bun'ei|ja|文永|qq=}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1273]] [[June 13]]) – {{ill|Hōjō Masamura|ja|北条政村|qq=}}, the 7th {{ill|Shikken|ja|執権|qq=}} of the {{ill|Kamakura shogunate|ja|鎌倉幕府|qq=}} (born [[1205]]).
