{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=五月廿七|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 5월 27일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 27''' is the 27th day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=|qq=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Tenpyō|ja|天平|qq=|qq=draft}} 15th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[743]] [[June 23]]) – {{ill|Konten Einnei Shizaihō|ja|墾田永年私財法|qq=|qq=draft}} の勅令。開墾した土地の私有を許可. * {{ill|Juei|ja|寿永|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1182]] [[June 29]]) – 兵乱と {{ill|Sangō no Yaku|ja|三合の厄|qq=|qq=draft}} を避ける為、{{ill|Yōwa|ja|養和|qq=|qq=draft}} より {{ill|Juei|ja|寿永|qq=|qq=draft}} に {{ill|Era change|ja|改元|qq=|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Eiwa|ja|永和|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year/{{ill|Tenshu|ja|天授|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1375]] [[June 26]]) – {{ill|Southern Court|ja|南朝|qq=|qq=draft}} が {{ill|Bunchū|ja|文中|qq=|qq=draft}} より {{ill|Tenshu|ja|天授|qq=|qq=draft}} に {{ill|Era change|ja|改元|qq=|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=|qq=draft}} 3rd year (閏5月) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1846]] [[July 20]]) – The American East India Squadron commander, Admiral {{ill|James Biddle|ja|ジェームズ・ビドル|qq=|qq=draft}}, arrives in Uraga and requests trade. The shogunate refuses.
== Births == * {{ill|Kenchō|ja|建暦|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1249]] [[July 9]]) – {{ill|Kameyama Tennō|ja|亀山天皇|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 90th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|qq=|qq=draft}} (died [[1305]]). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1868]] [[July 16]]) – {{ill|Hirose Takeo|ja|広瀬武夫|qq=|qq=draft}}, a member of the {{ill|Navy|ja|海軍|qq=|qq=draft}} and a military personnel who became known as the first {{ill|Military Deity|ja|軍神|qq=|qq=draft}} during the {{ill|Russo-Japanese War|ja|日露戦争|qq=|qq=draft}} (died [[1904]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Bun'ei|ja|文永|qq=|qq=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1273]] [[June 13]]) – {{ill|Hōjō Masamura|ja|北条政村|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 7th {{ill|Shikken|ja|執権|qq=|qq=draft}} of the {{ill|Kamakura shogunate|ja|鎌倉幕府|qq=|qq=draft}} (born [[1205]]).
