== Events == * {{ill|Tenpyō|ja|天平|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpyō|qq=}} 15th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[743]] [[June 23]]) – {{ill|Konten Einnei Shizaihō|ja|墾田永年私財法|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Konten Einnei Shizaihō|qq=}} の勅令。開墾した土地の私有を許可. * {{ill|Juei|ja|寿永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Juei|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1182]] [[June 29]]) – 兵乱と {{ill|Sangō no Yaku|ja|三合の厄|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sangō no Yaku|qq=}} を避ける為、{{ill|Yōwa|ja|養和|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yōwa|qq=}} より {{ill|Juei|ja|寿永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Juei|qq=}} に {{ill|Era change|ja|改元|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Era change|qq=}}. * {{ill|Eiwa|ja|永和|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eiwa|qq=}} 1st year/{{ill|Tenshu|ja|天授|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshu|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1375]] [[June 26]]) – {{ill|Southern Court|ja|南朝|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Southern Court|qq=}} が {{ill|Bunchū|ja|文中|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunchū|qq=}} より {{ill|Tenshu|ja|天授|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshu|qq=}} に {{ill|Era change|ja|改元|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Era change|qq=}}. * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōka|qq=}} 3rd year (閏5月) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1846]] [[July 20]]) – The American East India Squadron commander, Admiral {{ill|James Biddle|ja|ジェームズ・ビドル|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/James Biddle|qq=}}, arrives in Uraga and requests trade. The shogunate refuses.
== Births == * {{ill|Kenchō|ja|建暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kenchō|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1249]] [[July 9]]) – {{ill|Kameyama Tennō|ja|亀山天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kameyama Tennō|qq=}}, the 90th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor of Japan|qq=}} (died [[1305]]). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1868]] [[July 16]]) – {{ill|Hirose Takeo|ja|広瀬武夫|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hirose Takeo|qq=}}, a member of the {{ill|Navy|ja|海軍|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Navy|qq=}} and a military personnel who became known as the first {{ill|Military Deity|ja|軍神|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Military Deity|qq=}} during the {{ill|Russo-Japanese War|ja|日露戦争|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Russo-Japanese War|qq=}} (died [[1904]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Bun'ei|ja|文永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bun'ei|qq=}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1273]] [[June 13]]) – {{ill|Hōjō Masamura|ja|北条政村|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōjō Masamura|qq=}}, the 7th {{ill|Shikken|1=Shikken|2=ja|3=執権|ja|執権|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shikken|qq=}} of the {{ill|Kamakura shogunate|ja|鎌倉幕府|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamakura shogunate|qq=}} (born [[1205]]).
