== Events == * [[:en:Tenpyō|Tenpyō]] 15th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:743|743]] [[:en:June 23|June 23]]) – {{ill|Konten Einnei Shizaihō|ja|墾田永年私財法|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Konten Einnei Shizaihō|qq=}} の勅令。開墾した土地の私有を許可. * [[:en:Juei|Juei]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1182|1182]] [[:en:June 29|June 29]]) – 兵乱と {{ill|Sangō no Yaku|ja|三合の厄|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sangō no Yaku|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} を避ける為、[[:en:Yōwa|Yōwa]] より [[:en:Juei|Juei]] に {{ill|Era change|ja|改元|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Era change|qq=}}. * {{ill|Eiwa|ja|永和|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eiwa|qq=}} 1st year/[[:en:Tianshou|Tenshu]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1375|1375]] [[:en:June 26|June 26]]) – {{ill|Southern Court|ja|南朝|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Southern Court|qq=}} が [[:en:Bunchū|Bunchū]] より [[:en:Tianshou|Tenshu]] に {{ill|Era change|ja|改元|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Era change|qq=}}. * [[:en:Kōka|Kōka]] 3rd year (閏5月) ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1846|1846]] [[:en:July 20|July 20]]) – The American East India Squadron commander, Admiral [[:en:James Biddle|James Biddle]], arrives in Uraga and requests trade. The shogunate refuses.
== Births == * [[:en:Kenryaku|Kenchō]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1249|1249]] [[:en:July 9|July 9]]) – [[:en:Emperor Kameyama|Kameyama Tennō]], the 90th [[:en:Emperor of Japan|Emperor of Japan]] (died [[:en:1305|1305]]). * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1868|1868]] [[:en:July 16|July 16]]) – [[:en:Hirose Takeo|Hirose Takeo]], a member of the [[:en:Navy|Navy]] and a military personnel who became known as the first {{ill|Military Deity|ja|軍神|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Military Deity|qq=}} during the [[:en:Russo-Japanese War|Russo-Japanese War]] (died [[:en:1904|1904]]).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Bun'ei|Bun'ei]] 10th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1273|1273]] [[:en:June 13|June 13]]) – [[:en:Hōjō Masamura|Hōjō Masamura]], the 7th [[:en:Shikken|Shikken]] of the [[:en:Kamakura shogunate|Kamakura shogunate]] (born [[:en:1205|1205]]).
